{"tid":870970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[鬼城] 北京空置率或達20% 住建部前副部長倡徵空置稅","createTime":"2018-10-21T14:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T07:42:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2fe694c3bf051ad0c79c81fa527b03a2a8334d","tid":870970,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:10:39.000Z","msg":"北京空置率或達20% 住建部前副部長倡徵空置稅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2183297/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%8E%87%E6%88%96%E9%81%9420-%20%E4%BD%8F%E5%BB%BA%E9%83%A8%E5%89%8D%E5%89%AF%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E5%80%A1%E5%BE%B5%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%A8%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2183297%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%258E%2587%25E6%2588%2596%25E9%2581%259420-%2520%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%2589%25AF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%2580%25A1%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E7%25A8%2585&d=sxJE5pEKs1Lj8wXYeMwTMQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=7049a2b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2183297/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%8E%87%E6%88%96%E9%81%9420-%20%E4%BD%8F%E5%BB%BA%E9%83%A8%E5%89%8D%E5%89%AF%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E5%80%A1%E5%BE%B5%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%A8%85</a><br />\n<br />\n國務院參事、住房和城鄉建設部前副部長仇保興近日表示，遏制房地產投機、泡沫是個長期艱鉅的任務，應將房地產稅分類進行，率先推出能夠精準遏制投機的消費稅、流轉稅、空置稅，再從容考慮物業稅。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仇保興表示，中國房屋空置率比較高，不同城市空置率是不一樣的，像鄂爾多斯空置率是70%，北京空置率在百分之10幾到20。而從國際上看，一般採取了空置稅的國家空置率接近5%左右。<br />\n</span><br />\n<strong>房地產稅拆成四個稅 燙平泡沫</strong><br />\n<br />\n至於上述四種稅收，仇保興表示物業稅可以等5年，幾年以後慢慢考慮。前三種稅先行，房地產泡沫就可以燙平而不是刺破，對於保持居民消費能力和財富存量是很有好處的。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，房地產泡沫形成由來已久，針對衡量泡沫的收入房價比，他說：「在中國的國情下，十倍左右或者再多一點，問題不大，但現在有的城市已經高於二十倍。」他指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">尤其中國百姓的財富70%在房產裡，這個情況下貿然把泡沫刺破，會造成重要影響。</span><br />\n<br />\n他認為，要把房地產調控從原來的中央調為主轉變為地方調，從行政手段調為主變為經濟手段，從集中統一調變為分散調，通過國民經濟收入的增長來，嚴格控制樓價的漲幅，房地產泡沫要逐漸地燙平，而不是一腳踢破。"},{"pid":"c23825dbe07b496c983c29cbf02779ddf0ab757c","tid":870970,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:16:19.000Z","msg":"同香港一樣淨係徵發展商咪得"},{"pid":"f738cc2a10998b3a3c2fb73e3836c558acde827c","tid":870970,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T14:17:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14481cae689dd90ca566091570781b82b43fb7e7","tid":870970,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0aadd34fafbf13ef175083f2490600b3e568c13","tid":870970,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:19:12.000Z","msg":"習仔:yes又有得補血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b530c73996365c8ceb38a7a35998ce5feb89b2b","tid":870970,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:26:02.000Z","msg":"間中入去住一晚咪唔算空置"},{"pid":"7da3fe8dff835836417be1a1bfbdb2d5f73db98d","tid":870970,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:43:04.000Z","msg":"徵稅加二手樓限售（防止樓價大跌引爆泡沫）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064b1ab1041e4d1a52d4607d402453bd64b9c558","tid":870970,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:44:13.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"72083f14a214c401972ced7827bf5506dc22a73c","tid":870970,"uid":46933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:44:29.000Z","msg":"又要印錢又要打房<br />\n真係好大挑戰"},{"pid":"b44d2e637e986ca304a1654c61b5dc93d4e2339f","tid":870970,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b530c73996365c8ceb38a7a35998ce5feb89b2b","tid":870970,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T01:26:02.000Z","msg":"間中入去住一晚咪唔算空置"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T02:45:35.000Z","msg":"要加監控系統check